    "body": "Hi @MarshallOfSound . Thanks for the answer, but I'm using it to test the fix in this way:\n\n```\napp.on('activate', (e) => {\n  e.preventDefault();\n  app.show();\n  app.focus();\n});\n```\n\nand\n\n```\n  mainWindow.on('activate', () => {\n    mainWindow.restore();\n    mainWindow.focus();\n    mainWindow.show();\n  });\n\n```\n\nBut the issue persists. am I doing it wrong?\n"
