    "body": "The second one looks like it should work.  For reference the code I use it\n\n``` js\nimport { app } from 'electron';\n\napp.on('activate', () => {\n  const mainWindow = WindowManager.getAll('main')[0];\n  if (mainWindow) {\n    mainWindow.show();\n  } else {\n    // Something went wrong\n    app.quit();\n  }\n});\n```\n"
