    "body": "@MarshallOfSound I've discovered the problem. It's an always on top bug. It's needed to disable it before minimize the window. So, that's solve the problem on the app level:\n\n``` javascript\n  ipcMain.on('minimize-main-window', () => {\n    mainWindow.setAlwaysOnTop(false);\n    mainWindow.minimize();\n  });\n\n```\n\n``` javascript\napp.on('activate', () => {\n  mainWindow.restore();\n  mainWindow.setAlwaysOnTop(true);\n});\n```\n"
  }
